frontend/node_modules/
**/node_modules/
frontend/dist/
**/dist/
frontend/.vite/
**/.vite/
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*
**/pnpm-debug.log*

# --- Python ---
**/__pycache__/
**/*.py[cod]
.venv/
venv/
ENV/
env/

